b'Disability and Human Development'
b'Admissions and Programs'
b'PhD in Disability Studies'
b'Promoting the full participation, self-determination and equal citizenship of people with disabilities'
b'Disability studies scholars view disability not simply as a defect inside a person, but as a complex relationship between society and people who function differently from the norm.'
b'UIC\xe2\x80\x99s PhD in\xc2\xa0disability\xc2\xa0studies program addresses\xc2\xa0disability in its full complexity,\xc2\xa0promoting an awareness of disability that supports individuals in shaping their identities and lives.\xc2\xa0We examine how support\xc2\xa0services and\xc2\xa0social and political change can reduce sources of disempowerment.'
b'Disability studies at UIC offers a unique opportunity to study the multilayered, interactional dynamics\xc2\xa0of disability.'
